text: A lok-lok stand in Malacca Lok-lok is a dish consisting of various steamboat style foods inclusive of meats and vegetables that are served on a skewer in mobile form. It is a street food in Malaysia, in cities such as Penang, Kuching, among other places. ==See also== * List of street foods ==References== ==Further reading== * Category:Chinese cuisine Category:Street food
title: Lok-lok
